Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.11,0:00:03.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, all you viewers out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.83,0:00:07.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make \Nsure to keep the room nice and bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.13,0:00:09.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and sit back from the screen, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.39,0:00:13.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.94,0:00:16.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.27,0:00:20.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people who claimed to be Erza's old pals
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.42,0:00:23.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,appeared in front of us while we \Nwere at Akane beach on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.16,0:00:27.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see... Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.33,0:00:29.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And in no time at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.22,0:00:53.63,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all right! I'll yell it out countless times.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.63,0:00:58.70,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe your every tomorrow will be shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:01.05,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The intersection of all people
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.05,0:01:03.66,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,whose dreams have come true is one point:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:08.29,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Never giving up.  And that's why we're not gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:13.47,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,When it seems like you'll be blown away by the headwinds,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.47,0:01:15.62,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,grasp this hand, try to take a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.62,0:01:18.89,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're not alone anymore, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.01,0:01:24.00,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Go forward, more and more!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:26.52,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up on your awesome dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.52,0:01:27.78,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:29.25,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Move on, my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.25,0:01:31.63,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, with the light shining down upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.63,0:01:33.71,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even think about something like giving up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.71,0:01:36.14,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you trade being hurt again for strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.14,0:01:41.63,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes, always looking straight ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.63,0:01:45.91,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,can surely see the light!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.51,0:02:06.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It still exists? Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:12.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The R-system, that a black-magic cult \Nplotted to construct around ten years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.16,0:02:17.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we had destroyed \Nthe seven towers ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.62,0:02:21.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There was an eighth tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.03,0:02:23.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In the Ka Elm Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.06,0:02:26.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at it... Could it be complete?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.32,0:02:31.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The investigation team went missing \Nright after they sent these pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.49,0:02:33.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're finishing it, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.61,0:02:37.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the R-system now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.54,0:02:39.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Tower of Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.70,0:02:44.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not the R-system, the Tower of Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:46.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares what we call it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:48.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's forbidden magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.78,0:02:51.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If even its existence were known, \Nit would cause a huge uproar!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:56.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We must send the military \Nimmediately and suppress them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:58.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But we're up against...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.02,0:02:59.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:03.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The incident that occurred \Non Akane beach last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:05.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,According to reports from \Nwitness vacationers there,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.93,0:03:10.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it seems the people occupying the \NR-system now are not that magical cult.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:13.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, wait! Who in the world is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.85,0:03:17.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like that person is \Ngoing by the name of Jellal...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:19.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:23.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your twin brother, right, Siegrain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:27.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... I am aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.83,0:03:34.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:42.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you think the people \Ntrapped in the cards were saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:45.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We alerted the army, so \Nthey're probably fine by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:46.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.31,0:03:49.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But anyway, where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:52.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps Juvia's group has gotten lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.70,0:03:55.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, are you sure they're \Nin this direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:58.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're relying on your nose here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:03:59.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it together, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.85,0:04:02.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not allow you to \Nbetray Gray-sama's trust!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:04.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:08.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that Erza and Happy were \Nkidnapped while we were knocked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:09.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:14.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But how did a wizard as powerful \Nas Erza-san get defeated?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.11,0:04:16.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She wasn't defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:18.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know a damn thing about Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:20.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:22.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:27.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they were Erza's old friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:32.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even we don't know anything \Nabout Erza, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.07,0:04:38.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Something feels really dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:45.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The birds...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:46.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.06,0:04:49.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The fish too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.48,0:04:51.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.59,0:04:54.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This wreckage... It's from \NFiore military ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:55.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:57.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:02.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Tower of Heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:05.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Water Dome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:10.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us camouflage ourselves \Nthis way and approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:12.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:18.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You actually completed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.77,0:05:21.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been eight years since then, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.39,0:05:23.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We completed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:27.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight years...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.14,0:05:29.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys have all changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.59,0:05:31.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:33.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost there, sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:36.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have any sense \Nof dramatic tension?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:39.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The ceremony will take place tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:42.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Until then, stay right here, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:43.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.95,0:05:46.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to activate the R-system?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:50.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad, you know? It's your \Nfault for betraying us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:54.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal is angry. But it's an honor for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:57.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been chosen as the living \Nsacrifice for the ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.86,0:06:01.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I won't get to see you again, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:03.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But we do it all for paradise...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:07.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're shaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.10,0:06:09.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Scared of becoming a living sacrifice?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:13.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it because this is the very place...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:22.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can escape so \Neasily, you little brats?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:27.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At a time when we need to \Nfinish the R-System quicky!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:30.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up... At this rate we'd \Nget way behind schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.93,0:06:33.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to send you \Nall to that room, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.61,0:06:38.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is the one who came up with the escape \Nplan? I'll only take that one away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:40.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we such nice guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:43.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Spit it out! Who is the mastermind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:46.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.54,0:06:46.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:50.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I made the plan, and I told them what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.49,0:06:54.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:56.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't you, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:58.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:06:59.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take her away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:03.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It was me! I planned it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:04.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:05.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let Erza go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:09.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:11.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:13.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:18.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be just like you said, \NJellal... I'm not scared at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:20.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:22.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.03,0:07:27.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about back then, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:32.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who planned it, but I \Nwas scared and didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.62,0:07:35.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.96,0:07:40.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's long in the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:45.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand the danger of trying \Nto resurrect someone using the R-system?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:50.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what the R-system \Nis for? I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:52.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Revive System...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.21,0:07:56.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To resurrect a single person using a \Nlarge number of human sacrifices...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:07:58.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's forbidden, inhumane magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:08:02.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister... Magic has always \Nbeen at odds with humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:06.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All magic erodes one's humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:10.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's black-magic sophism. \NYou're no different from them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:13.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They thought this was just a \Nway to reunite body with soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.83,0:08:17.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't realize it was more than just \Nmagic to bring someone back from the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:19.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Jellal is different!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.84,0:08:23.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be leading us to heaven shortly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:24.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:29.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When Jellal resurrects that certain \Nindividual, the world will be reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:32.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With us as its rulers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:35.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The last remnants of the cult \Nwho took away our freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.44,0:08:38.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You, my trator Sister and your friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:41.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The pitiful citizens living \Ntheir lives in ignorance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.17,0:08:44.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those incompetent fools on the Council!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:47.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They will all cower in \Nfear, be drenched in grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:50.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll take away everyone's freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:55.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We will become the rulers of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:03.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:07.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sho...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.47,0:09:11.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.37,0:09:16.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To think people can change so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:21.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:22.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this your doing, you fiend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.12,0:09:31.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all cats!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:33.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:34.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:36.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a cat-woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:38.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Feelin' spiffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:40.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Feelin' spiffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:43.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a talking kitty cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:47.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Millianna, why don't you \Ntry being more of a dandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:49.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:54.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't a talking cat. It's a \Ncat because it talks, get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:55.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:57.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get that at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:10:00.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And wait, where am I? Where's Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.34,0:10:05.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey cat! That boy is probably \Nkissing asphalt right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.89,0:10:09.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way Natsu's been done in like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.59,0:10:12.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a report! Erza Scarlet has escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.72,0:10:15.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Escaped? Just like old times!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:18.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no escape from this tower...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:19.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.85,0:10:22.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza's here too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.82,0:10:22.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.78,0:10:27.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Jellal...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:30.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew Erza would make a good woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:31.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How intriguing, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:36.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to see \Nwho wins: Erza or myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:38.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Life and death...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:42.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A game of heaven which \Nconnects the past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.54,0:10:45.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.61,0:10:46.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First, gather information!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:48.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We must dispatch the entire military!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:49.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You bleeding-heart doves...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:50.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.89,0:10:52.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sieg, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.26,0:10:54.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sending the military?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:56.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What else could I call someone \Nwith that weak a response?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.61,0:10:59.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is dangerous... Far too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.92,0:11:01.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:03.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You people don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:07.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is only one way to destroy \Nthe Tower of Heaven now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:10.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise we are all doomed for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:11.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Etherion!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:13.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:15.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The cross-dimensional destruction magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:16.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you mad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:18.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've seen its predicted \Ndestructive power, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:21.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It has the power to destroy \Nan entire country!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:24.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Etherion is our ultimate weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.84,0:11:27.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's even more dangerous \Nmagic than the R-system!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:28.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:34.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But with the satellite square, \Nwe could target this entire area.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:39.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the only thing that could destroy \Nsuch a large building is Etherion!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.81,0:11:41.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I concur.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.87,0:11:43.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultear, you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.71,0:11:46.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are 9 of us in total. \NOnly three more are needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.94,0:11:50.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If three more people agree \Nthan we fire Etherion!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.78,0:11:52.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:55.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let him use the R-system!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:12:01.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That will end with your twin brother \NJellal losing his life, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:02.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.77,0:12:06.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just how terrible a system it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:19.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me where Jellal is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:21.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of lookouts...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:22.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we bust in?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.43,0:12:25.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Erza and Happy are captured!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:28.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't do this right, we could \Nput the two of them in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.23,0:12:29.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That would put us at a disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:32.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've found a way in underwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:34.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:35.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been praised!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:38.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not you, but I, Juvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:38.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Riiight...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:41.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about ten minutes underwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.95,0:12:43.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That ain't a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.46,0:12:44.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:45.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:48.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then put this on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:52.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's oxygen trapped in a water shell, \Nso you can breath underwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:54.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:56.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So... Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.48,0:13:06.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is that base of the tower...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.69,0:13:08.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Erza and Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:10.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,These things are pretty \Nconvenient, if a bit tacky...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.69,0:13:15.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I made yours a bit smaller, Lucy-san, \Nso I'm impressed you made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.24,0:13:16.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a sec there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.39,0:13:18.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Intruders!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:19.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:24.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are these infidels!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:25.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.69,0:13:27.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...guess there's only one thing to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:27.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:29.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're asking who we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:33.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your allies attacked us, \Nand you don't even know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:36.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're Fairy Tail, you idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:38.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:41.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Lance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:41.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:43.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A swimsuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.62,0:13:44.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:46.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Maiden, I open thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.75,0:13:48.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Virgo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:51.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You called for me, Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:52.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.21,0:13:53.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who needs bikini-girl now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:55.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Proceed with the punishment, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:56.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.97,0:13:59.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, what is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.45,0:14:01.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, blades don't affect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:03.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:07.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:09.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Drip, drip, drop...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.02,0:14:11.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Water Slicer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:19.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're mostly finished here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:20.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.78,0:14:22.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After making all this noise, \Ndo you think we'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:23.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, who am I kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.83,0:14:24.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I need punishment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.95,0:14:26.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the blockhead?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:32.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:34.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're telling us, "Come on up?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:37.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Jellal, why are you \Ninviting the intruders inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:40.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, remember? This is a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:43.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They have cleared a stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:45.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:46.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This makes things more interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.92,0:14:49.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we don't hurry with the ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:53.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The ships we sunk the other day mean \Nthat the Council has already...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.56,0:14:57.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Vidaldus, are you still worried about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:00.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I concur!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:01.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elder Leiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.86,0:15:03.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:04.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Only two more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:06.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:08.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:11.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not those fools on the \NCouncil, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:15.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blockhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:16.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't yell like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:19.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We already made such a big mess downstairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:21.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason for us to \Nbe sneaking around anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:23.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:24.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like a meal has been prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:25.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall you partake, Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.79,0:15:27.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, look here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.35,0:15:31.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That door from before was operated \Nby remote control through magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:34.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our presence is completely known.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:35.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.65,0:15:37.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they're challenging us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:39.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:42.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes, Princess... Do you think it \Nis appropriate to eat in such attire?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.72,0:15:43.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Appropriate?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:45.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us change those clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.26,0:15:46.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.45,0:15:47.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:49.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama! Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:52.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,These are clothes from the Spirit World.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:56.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? I know, \NI know... I look good...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:15:58.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.73,0:16:00.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia is so frustrated!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:01.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He lllikes her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.47,0:16:03.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't roll your tongue...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.21,0:16:05.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you learn to mimic Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:10.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:12.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, I wish you best of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.51,0:16:14.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Virgo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:17.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, are you sure you \Nwant to stay in those wet clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:19.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll dry them off in a jiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:20.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Human drying machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:21.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.53,0:16:22.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The intruders!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:26.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:27.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:29.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:32.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.98,0:16:34.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:36.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Juvia is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:37.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:39.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a place you should have come!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.71,0:16:43.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go sayin' that, Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:44.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we retreat with our \Ntails between out legs,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.93,0:16:46.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,that'll shame the name of Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.89,0:16:49.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not going to let \Nthat Blockhead off easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:51.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:51.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.77,0:16:53.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy's been kidnapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:54.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You expect me to leave him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.94,0:16:55.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:58.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Millianna couldn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:16:59.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:01.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:01.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The ocean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:03.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.01,0:17:04.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:07.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy is waiting for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.45,0:17:08.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:10.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.26,0:17:11.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:12.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:14.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.19,0:17:16.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Millianna loves cats above all else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.58,0:17:19.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot believe that she \Nwould do harm to Happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.61,0:17:22.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take responsibility for \Nbringing both of them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.59,0:17:24.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You get away from here as quickly as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.59,0:17:26.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Not without you, Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:28.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:30.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not want to get you involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:33.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already plenty our problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:34.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw Natsu, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:39.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, what is this tower? Who is Jellal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.11,0:17:43.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand if you don't want to tell us...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:47.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that they used to \Nbe your companions, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:51.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But now we're your companions...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.08,0:17:54.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on your side, no matter what Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.39,0:17:55.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard the lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.83,0:17:57.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:17:58.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:01.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't like you, Ms. Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:05.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd usually say, "Follow \Nme and no complaining!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.72,0:18:08.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll lend you a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:12.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even you get scared sometimes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.86,0:18:20.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.67,0:18:27.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether I win or lose this battle, \NI will vanish from this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:28.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:32.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a future I cannot oppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.82,0:18:33.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.62,0:18:38.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore while I still exist, \NI'll tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.78,0:18:44.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The name of this tower \Nis the Tower of Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.57,0:18:46.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Also known as the R-system.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.55,0:18:49.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,More than ten years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:52.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A black-magic religious cult
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:57.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,constructed it in order to cast a forbidden \Nspell to resurrect someone from the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.19,0:19:02.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It requires a large number \Nof living sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.33,0:19:05.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, through the slave-labor \Nof the sacrificial humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:08.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,they amplified the magical power they needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.23,0:19:14.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was also one of those living \Nsacrifices when I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:18.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who tried to escape, or rebelled...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.64,0:19:21.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One by one they disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:24.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:26.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We lived in constant fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.09,0:19:30.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I made friends \Nwho I could open up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.79,0:19:33.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it was for only a brief moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:39.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And one of the people I knew then was Jellal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:46.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:48.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.11,0:19:51.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.01,0:19:56.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:02.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What have they done... Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:04.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What did we do to deserve this, Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:07.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:10.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:12.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:14.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay now. I've come to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:17.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:24.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no turning back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.96,0:20:26.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:27.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:32.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.68,0:20:34.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the magic troops!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.95,0:20:38.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Sis is okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:41.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Rob, you came back \Nalive from that room, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.59,0:20:42.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is that place...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.87,0:20:46.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Erza-chan should be fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.16,0:20:50.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you have a strong heart, \Nthey can't steal your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:52.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:52.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:54.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.89,0:20:56.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.14,0:20:58.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's Jellal?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:59.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for work!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.43,0:21:00.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave her be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.30,0:21:02.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just be glad she's back \Nalive at a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.73,0:21:04.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.12,0:21:07.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They must have taken a replacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.94,0:21:09.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No more...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:12.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.11,0:21:13.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:14.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Sho!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.89,0:21:18.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay... I'm here beside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.51,0:21:20.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:21.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.72,0:21:22.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:24.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.62,0:21:25.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:29.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.37,0:21:30.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.31,0:21:33.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're rebelling!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.84,0:21:36.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, what are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.18,0:21:37.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take their weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.55,0:21:41.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we obey them, or run \Naway, we'll never be free!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.26,0:21:43.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.04,0:21:46.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For our freedom, rise up and fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.86,0:21:52.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For our freedom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.58,0:21:56.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To save Jellal... We rose up and fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.66,0:22:02.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal was our leader... He had a strong \Nsense of justice, and I looked up to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.38,0:22:04.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.11,0:22:10.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was right at that moment that Jellal \Nturned into a completely different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:18.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If it is possible to call a person "evil," \Nthen that is what I shall call Jellal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.18,0:24:00.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, have you heard a strange \Nvoice at night lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.94,0:24:01.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A strange voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.92,0:24:03.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't heard anything weird myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.49,0:24:05.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.16,0:24:08.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Night after night, a girl's \Nvoice, softly sobbing...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.29,0:24:09.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.46,0:24:11.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds pretty cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.00,0:24:13.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's cool at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.96,0:24:16.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Voice of Darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.51,0:24:18.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what is that poltergeist saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.97,0:24:22.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"The rent... Oh, the rent!" etc...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.07,0:24:24.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure that's just Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.00,0:24:26.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
